Name: Cutie Tutti Frutti
About the game: 'Cutie Tutti Frutti' is a game based on '3 in a row' mechanics. The goal of match-3 puzzles is to make groups, lines and rows of 3 or more identical tiles. The player takes on the role of a cook who needs to collect the required amount of ingredients for a dish. As the difficulty increases further, more ingredients are required and their quantity also increases. Bonus tiles come to the rescue, such as a bomb, a knife, time freeze and other things. The level is considered completed if the time has not expired and all the ingredients are collected. Game Features: 25 levels with increasing difficulty Steam Achivements support Easy to learn gameplay Game makes you think fast
